INSERT INTO `first_verifications` VALUES (1,1,'Matest and Alteo structural Analysis for Rebound Hammer','N/A','Vendor accreditation ongoing for Matest and Alteo? Alteo Engineering Consultancy Services have been accredited on September 21, 2023. Matest have yet to submit an accreditation form Did the process owner meet with FAD to discuss accreditation procedures? Yes, instruction to inform was discussed on August 23, 2023; whenever there is a new third-party provider What is the status of the WI to establish the process of assisting FAD accredit new subcontractors The process owners recognized that the existing Procedure Manual )PM No. 07-02-02 - Handling outsourced products and Services providers) for the vendor accreditation is adequate as a guide for future accreditations','No new accreditation','N/A','Reverify on Oct 16,2023 - done','2024-11-06 16:00:00','2024-11-06 16:00:00'),(2,6,'Scheduled on 1/17/2024. Reverification as of January 22, 2024 and January 23, 2024. Topics discussed Measurement of Crane, Hoist, GENSET, Elevator, Manlift and Dumbwaiter as evidenced by the attendance. Five out of the 6 participants have retained and improved their knowledge on PTO process based on their examinations. See sample pre-test and post-test below.','Magna Prime outputs (Application, Plan and Specs) were found deficient in the first quality checking on November 30, 2023. Magna Prime outputs were sent to DOLE RO III on December 15, 2024','Self Internal Review Checklist is currently being used (trial). To be used per equipment set (separate sheet inside a file)','See CA info','Other users should be able to try to use the document. Cascading of the checklist shall be done on Jan 17, 2024','Reverification on January 17, 2024 - Done','2024-11-06 16:00:00','2024-11-06 16:00:00'),(3,7,'Verify all data entered into the KPI scorecard (2023) for the first-pass yield of plans/applications for any inaccuracies and revise appropriately Consolidated and reviewed data for 2023 of the ff KPIs: For Plans 2023 (March from 100% to 95%) For Applications 2023 pending April 30','N/A','See verification for correction above','Guidelines for document quality checking and its cascading -  Establish monitoring of raw data to achieve more accurate KPI results. The assigned Technical and Admin Support updates the google sheet entitled Consulting Internal Review Monitoring as displayed below: However, scores recorded in the Scorecard do not match the data from the Monitoring. Assigned personnel to update the score by April 30, 2024','Error-free Plans Monitoring for updating','For Further Verification','2024-11-06 16:00:00','2024-11-06 16:00:00'),(4,8,'Accomplished the review form to record the completion of the fourth round of quality checks of the documents.','Ensure that all comments from previous reviews are corrected and documented. See below for the Before and after','Revise existing internal review form (FM No. 06-01-24) to not limit review rounds to third reviews. Effective April 05, 2024 already used for the project below on April 08, 2024 Establish guidelines for document quality checking','N/A','N/A','For Further Verification','2024-11-06 16:00:00','2024-11-06 16:00:00'),(5,9,'Relocate obsolete forms to a separate folder, distinct from enrolled forms. Done. The Documentation Head and DDC of the department enforces use of DMS google site for the latest forms.','See correction','Restrict enrolled forms folder on NAS to exclusive access by Department DC and Documentation Head. The Documentation Head and DDC of the department enforces use of DMS google site for the latest forms. Issue an internal memo regarding item 1 Done. See image below. DDC and DC Head will conduct a short refresher/orientation on department document control','Ongoing review of processes','N/A','For Further Verification','2024-11-06 16:00:00','2024-11-06 16:00:00'),(6,11,'Revise IGR for tolerance for Metric Steel Tape under Metric Tape. The IGR No. 06-01-10 was revised in April. Changes